cz.cuni.mff.kocur.agent

Class TeamContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.cuni.mff.kocur.agent.TeamContext

  • public class TeamContext
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that represents team's context. Team context is a representation of a world that is inherent to every bot (that has a team). It's goal is to supply function that will help agents to navigate around the world.
    Author:
    kocur
